            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>長廣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7795:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7795\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7795-TW</a>)31日13:19下跌37元，股價跌停報337.0元，委買8張、委賣3張，成交461張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為機械設備製造與銷售。電子零組件製造與銷售。機械設備安裝。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>長廣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7795:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7795\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7795-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌7.31%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.62%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-425 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-426 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+2 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
